From: "Barak A. Pearlmutter" <barak@pearlmutter.net>
Date: Sat, 6 Jun 2026 20:01:53 +0100
Subject: include config.h not .../config.h

Need to #include "config.h" not "../config.h" or whatever. Automake
passes the right compiler options, so ../ is not necessary.
